title: Upscalien in da house
description: There once was an alien whose mother called him Trey, from the fanciest planet in the Milky Way. Stole his dad’s ship, took it for a trip, saw Lake Erie on his radar and he thought he’d take a dip.
altHero: an alien named Trey in a tuxedo stands cross-armed in front of his spaceship
alt1: Trey boards his ship on another planet with blue ground and orange sky
alt2: Trey navigates toward Earth and Lake Erie
alt3: Trey stands atop his ship in swim trunks
